TribeHR,uses,WebHooks,to,provide,real,time,callbacks,to,scripts,that,are,hosted,on,a,user,s,web,server,TribeHR,offers,a,secure,human,resources,website,platform,with,the,goal,of,simplifying,and,automating,many,common,HR,tasks,With,WebHooks,allows,the,creation,ofscripts,that,respond,to,actions,that,take,place,within,a,secure,and,private,human,resources,website